Buttons
 *clickablebooster

  name:The Booster

  desc:B

  on click:yield 1 boost

  class:bigButton

  Icon:https://i.imgur.com/1WIFxhd.png

  tooltip origin:bottom
  tooltip class:red

  show clicks

Resources
 *boost

  name:Boost Clicks

  desc:It may not affect on early game, however it would be must-need resource mid-game!

  Icon:debug[2,4]

 *flop

  name:Perfomance Currency

  desc:The power of FLOPs, bangwidth, and system stats shows it's pride. Effectively, it's transformed to the currency. Do the Personal Computing.
  
  start with:1

  Icon:debug[3,4]

 *byte

  name:Bytes

  desc:The ascension currency, with the greater benefit. Powers your building with the exchange of the soft reset.

  Icon:debug[4,4]
  
 *ach
 
  name:Achievements
  
  always hidden
  
 *poor
  
  name:Poor achievement
  
  always hidden
  
 *destitute
  
  name:Destitute achievement
  
  always hidden
  
 *decent
  
  name:Decent achievement
  
  always hidden
  
 *minimum
  
  name:At-least-you-tried achievement
  
  always hidden

Buildings

 *i386

  name:Intel 80386

  desc:Effect on updates, First level 

  cost:1 flop

  Icon:debug[0,1]
  
  on tick:yield 1 flop

  show max

Upgrades

 *386OS1

  name:Windows/386 Version 2.03

  desc:Powering Intel 80308 with increased X1.4 perfomance

  cost:3 flop

  passive:multiply yield of i386 by 1.4

  req:1 i386

  Icon:debug[2,3] debug[1,2]
  
Achievements

 *flopM1
 
  name:First try
  
  desc:Have <b>1 unit</b> of perfomance currency.
  
  req:1 flop
  
  icon:icons[3,4] icons[0,0]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 poor
  
 *click1
 
  name:We're just starting!
  
  desc:Clicked <b>15</b> times to boost
  
  req:15 boost
  
  icon:icons[2,4] icons[0,0]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 poor
  
 *click2
 
  name:And yet we're still here!
  
  desc:Clicked <b>100</b> times to boost
  
  req:100 boost
  
  icon:icons[2,4] icons[1,0]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 destitute
  
 *click3
 
  name:Click to go
  
  desc:Clicked <b>300</b> times to boost
  
  req:300 boost
  
  icon:icons[2,4] icons[2,0]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 decent
  
 *click4
 
  name:You're clicking still
  
  desc:Clicked <b>1000</b> times to boost
  
  req:1000 boost
  
  icon:icons[2,4] icons[3,0]
  
  on earn:yield 1 ach
  on earn:yield 1 minimum
